scene_description: There are nine spaces organized into three rows and three columns. Some spaces are filled with a shape, other spaces are left blank. The spaces are created by grid-like lines of one color, which can reappear as shapes within the cells as well.
literal_instruction: There are nine spaces organized into three rows and three columns. Some spaces are filled with a shape, other spaces are left blank. For each of the blank spaces, copy the shape found in the space in the top left corner.
